title: Build Yourself
itunes:title: Build Yourself
description:
Episode 176 - A lot of people think that the way they are is the way they will always be. If you look at successful people, though, they consciously "build themselves" every day. They know who they want to be, then they focus on building themselves into that person. In this episode I talk about how to build the person you want to become.
